<h2><b>Why Choose Himalayan Hikers?</b></h2>
<ul>
 	<li>Experienced local guides</li>
 	<li>Safety-first approach (pulse oximeters, first-aid, evacuation support)</li>
 	<li>Eco-friendly trekking</li>
 	<li>Homely food and family-style hospitality</li>
 	<li>Affordable, all-inclusive packages</li>
 	<li>Trusted by <strong>1500+ trekkers</strong> every year who choose the <strong>Valley of Flowers Trek</strong> and <strong>Hemkund Sahib Yatra</strong> for an unforgettable Himalayan journey.</li>
</ul>
